<h1>40 Hours Is Breaking Even</h1>
<p><img src="http://media.tumblr.com/tumblr_laydibduts1qzbc4f.jpg" alt=""></p>
<p>I read an article yesterday that made a great point. Unfortunately, I
don’t remember the link. But the point was that to get ahead in life you
must put in more than 40 hours. I know, it sounds so simple, but yet so
many people don’t think this way.</p>
<p>Whatever your career is, you must put in more than 40 hours. Maybe you
want a promotion? Maybe you want to build a company? Just remember, 40
hours is breaking even.</p>
